{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d426d0127f","title":"反围攻时给红军的动员令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6866ef9c4b","type":"title","text":"反围攻时给红军的动员令","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"d426d0127f"},{"id":"1a91e87c62","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人已经向我们的基本苏区大举进攻了，我们无论如何要战胜这个敌人。我们要用一切坚定性顽强性持久性去战胜这个敌人。我们这样做就是能够最后的战胜这个敌人。最后的胜利是我们的。英勇奋斗的红军万岁！","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"d426d0127f"},{"id":"b1c6ea9470","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"d426d0127f"},{"id":"e3f3e17ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自《中国新民主主义革命时期历史》“初稿”）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"d426d0127f"}],"page":{"id":"f2fb69208b","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"d426d0127f","start":211,"end":211}}}},"__N_SSG":true}